      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEFORE THE DAWN (1) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.77 beating Linkin Park. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Well placed and will be tough to beat. CAWBOURNE ZARA (8) has a strong winning strike-rate over this journey with two wins and a placing from four tries. Comes off a (24.91) win last time, scoring by half a length in a Grade 5 over 440m at Goulburn. Can feature with the right run. TAKE A BREAK (2) has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (30.20) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Wentworth Park. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. ZIPPING CRUELLA (3) will make her presence felt following a brief layoff.",
